Inspektur!

291
00:19:44,542 --> 00:19:46,260
Ada apa?

292
00:19:46,261 --> 00:19:47,501
Kami menemukan sidik jari.

293
00:19:47,821 --> 00:19:51,590
Sidik jari Ishizawa di bom yang ada di TKP Suemura.

294
00:19:51,591 --> 00:19:52,381
Apa?

